node.text:
I tried making the Mason Jar Ice Cream it was so yummy! Mix 5 ingredients into a mason jar, shake for 5 minutes, and then put in the freezer for a couple hours! 

Cookies & Cream Ingredients: 
-1 cup heavy cream
-1 ½ tablespoons granulated sugar
-1 ½ teaspoons vanilla extract
-A pinch of salt
-3 crushed Oreos

node.text:
Some of these gadgets were amazing! ❤️

Watch full video on my YouTube channel! Thanks @ijustine for helping me!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Rosanna Pansino on July 10, 2021 tagging @ijustine. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: My friend @ijustine introduced me to lightsaber training for the first time! It was so fun! Go watch the video on her channel!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Rosanna Pansino on July 05, 2021 tagging @ijustine, @frmheadtotoe, @laurajquinn, @mollyluwho, and @blueandcoconut. May be an image of 5 people, people sitting, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: My heart is so full and happy! Very grateful to be able to spend the 4th of July with friends again! Love you all so much! ❤️
